ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:

This software is based on bolt.diy (https://github.com/stackblitz-labs/bolt.diy)
originally created by Cole Medin and contributors.

Wetware Studio enhancements include:
- Universal project compatibility auto-fixing
- Next.js version management (automatic downgrade from v16 to v15)
- Tailwind CSS v3/v4 auto-detection and configuration
- Enhanced WebGL, Three.js, and WebGPU support
- Smart PostCSS configuration handling
- React version compatibility management
- 20+ automatic compatibility fixes
